        <abstract>
            <p>CD despairs when men like AG and Lyell consider themselves incapable of judging on change of species by descent.</p>
            <p>Is confused over phyllotaxy.</p> 
<p>Has been looking at <hi rend="italic">Plantago lanceolata</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
